<div class="note" topic="statutoryNotes"><span class="heading centered"><strong>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</strong></span></div>
<div class="note" topic="changeOfName">
<span class="heading centered smallCaps">Change of Name</span>
<p>Committee on Small Business of <span link="https://liicornell.org/liifedent/cong_senate" occur="10" src="named_federal_agencies">Senate</span> changed to Committee on Small Business and Entrepreneurship of <span link="https://liicornell.org/liifedent/cong_senate" occur="11" src="named_federal_agencies">Senate</span>. See <span link="https://liicornell.org/liifedent/cong_senate" occur="12" src="named_federal_agencies">Senate</span> Resolution No. 123, One Hundred Seventh <span link="https://liicornell.org/liifedent/congress" occur="5" src="named_federal_agencies">Congress</span>, <span class="date" date="2001-06-29">June 29, 2001</span>. Previously, Select Committee on Small Business of <span link="https://liicornell.org/liifedent/cong_senate" occur="13" src="named_federal_agencies">Senate</span> became Committee on Small Business of <span link="https://liicornell.org/liifedent/cong_senate" occur="14" src="named_federal_agencies">Senate</span>. See <span link="https://liicornell.org/liifedent/cong_senate" occur="15" src="named_federal_agencies">Senate</span> Resolution No. 101, Ninety-Seventh <span link="https://liicornell.org/liifedent/congress" occur="6" src="named_federal_agencies">Congress</span>, <span class="date" date="1981-03-25">Mar. 25, 1981</span>.</p>
